etomica.models.oneDHardRods

Class MeterDifferentImageAddDoubleSize

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.data.DataSourceScalar
      • etomica.models.oneDHardRods.MeterDifferentImageAdd
        • etomica.models.oneDHardRods.MeterDifferentImageAddDoubleSize
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDataSource, IEtomicaDataSource

    public class MeterDifferentImageAddDoubleSize
extends MeterDifferentImageAdd
    Uses a Widom-like insertion of a mode to calculate a probability. Uses a different box than the main simulation, to assume an extra mode & rod are added Should only be used when one system is exactly twice the size of the other system.
